track_notes: Plenty room to park the car at Castillon, the path easy and at summit there is an old Fort, and pylone. Plenty room for antenna

This time i parked at the Col des Banquettes, plenty room for car, the sloope is hard on the path, but you can use the road at the beginning. Near the summit you must look for the path in between trees and rocks. On summit there are many antenna system, and also plenty room for setup your antenna! I used this way down i did not know; as rain has fallen, the rocks were very sliding (rolling stone) hi!!!
track_title: Nice walk but summit is no a must.
